## OMNI CRASH FIX (Critical)
- **Root cause:** `UserModal.jsx` called `useSovereign()` hook without importing it — caused `ReferenceError` on every render, crashing entire React tree with black screen
- **Fix:** Added `import { useSovereign } from '../context/SovereignContext'`
- **Secondary fix:** Modal title said `"Oracle"` → corrected to `"Omni"`
- **Rebuild:** `npm run build:dev` ran successfully, new bundle `dist-dev/assets/index-c3b46add.js` deployed

